{
  "texts": [
    "The cells were passaged with ReleSR (Stemcell Technologies, Cat#05872) as small colonies after reaching 70-80% confluency.",
    "3 μM of CHIR99021 (Tocris Bioscience, Minneapolis, USA, Cat#4423) and 1 μM of PD0325901 (Selleckchem, Houston, USA, Cat#S1036) 19 were added to the culture medium of PTN iPSCs.",
    "The cultures were regularly tested for mycoplasma contamination.",
    "The gRNAs targeting respective tumor suppressor genes were inserted into modified pX330 plasmids 56 containing the puromycin-resistant gene.",
    "The electroporation was conducted with Neon™ Transfection System (Thermo Fisher Scientific, Massachusetts, USA)."
  ]
}